			                        <h1>Bill Of Materials (BOM) Placidus</h1>
                                    
                        
              <div class="region region-content">
    <div id="block-system-main" class="block block-system">


<div class="content">
<div id="node-13" class="node node-page" about="/web/en/content/bill-materials-bom-placidus" typeof="foaf:Document">

  
      <span property="dc:title" content="Bill Of Materials (BOM) Placidus" class="rdf-meta element-hidden"></span>
  
  <div class="content clearfix">
    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"><p>This is a list of things which can be used to build an Escornabot. Of course, you can build it with other things, that's the beauty of an Open Source project, but if you want to stick to the basics, here's what we use...</p>

<h2>For the escornabot</h2>

<table><thead><tr><th align="left">Thing</th>
  <th align="center">How many?</th>
</tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left"><a href="http://www.ebay.com/sch/i.html?_from=R40&amp;_trksid=p2047675.m570.l1313.TR0.TRC0.H0.X5v+28byj-48.TRS0&amp;_nkw=5v+28byj-48&amp;ghostText=&amp;_sacat=0">5V 28BYJ-48 Stepper Motors with their ULN2003 drivers</a></td>
  <td align="center">2</td>
</tr><tr><td align="left"><a href="http://arduino.cc/en/Main/arduinoBoardNano">Arduino Nano</a> or <a href="http://arduino.cc/en/Products.Compare">similar</a></td>
  <td align="center">1</td>
</tr><tr><td align="left"><a href="http://www.ebay.com/sch/i.html?_odkw=5v+28byj-48&amp;_from=R40&amp;_osacat=0&amp;_from=R40&amp;_trksid=p2045573.m570.l1313.TR0.TRC0.H0.X170+pts+breadboard.TRS0&amp;_nkw=170+pts+breadboard&amp;ghostText=&amp;_sacat=0">170 pts Breadboard</a></td>
  <td align="center">1</td>
</tr><tr><td align="left"><a href="http://www.ebay.com/sch/i.html?_odkw=buzzer+5v+active&amp;_from=R40|R40|R40|R40|R40&amp;_osacat=0&amp;_from=R40&amp;_trksid=p2045573.m570.l1313.TR0.TRC0.H0.X+5v+active+buzzer.TRS1&amp;_nkw=+5v+active+buzzer&amp;ghostText=&amp;_sacat=0">5V Active Buzzer</a></td>
