</tr><tr><td align="left"><a href="http://www.ebay.com/sch/i.html?_odkw=zip+ties+100x2%2C5mm&amp;_from=R40|R40|R40|R40|R40|R40|R40|R40&amp;_osacat=0&amp;_from=R40&amp;_trksid=p2045573.m570.l1313.TR0.TRC0.H0.Xzip+ties+2.5mm.TRS0&amp;_nkw=zip+ties+2.5mm&amp;ghostText=&amp;_sacat=0">2.5 mm Zip Ties</a>(10 cm or so)</td>
